s, men det hadde v\u00e6rt enda mer uheldig for syklistene. Det er mer trafikk der enn tillatt, men det er fordi folk ikke respekterer skiltene, sier Vodal."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "ae898bef33598e0627a3bff674b07d8e9e5b360c0a3d302cc44438dd1639d4e0"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-02T06:33:58.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Drosjer og privatbiler kj\u00f8rer ulovlig for \u00e5 komme seg til hurtigb\u00e5tterminalen i Trondheim."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article12630156.ece/6ztk8y/ALTERNATES/w980-default/sladdterminalen.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/54bfa184a5fdc622cc19bcde01f313afcebed5b8.jpg?598c98b3"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Sv\u00e6rt uheldig \u00e5 ha en b\u00e5tterminal uten kj\u00f8readkomst -adressa.no", "- Viktig sykkelrute", "- Kjempeutfordring", "- F\u00e5r ikke gjort jobben", "Jobbet med skiltingen"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "54bfa184a5fdc622cc19bcde01f313afcebed5b8"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["sykkel", "trondheim", "Parkering"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "sykkel,trondheim,Parkering"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["trondheim kommune", "terminalen", "trondheim", "privatbiler kj\u00f8rer", "kj\u00f8re", "drosjer", "jobbet"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["adresseavisen", "pluss", "tr\u00f8ndertaxi", "bratt\u00f8rkaia", "parkering", "parkeringsvaktene"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["tr\u00f8ndelag", "trondheim", "ila"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["anders maurin